Package btrplace.solver.choco

Choco implementation of a ReconfigurationAlgorithm.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ChocoReconfigurationAlgorithm
    A reconfiguration algorithm based on the Choco constraint solver.
    ChocoReconfigurationAlgorithmParams
    Parameters for a ChocoReconfigurationAlgorithm.
    MisplacedVMsEstimator
    An interface to specify an object that can estimated a supposed set of misplaced VMs in a model.
    ObjectiveAlterer
    A class to provide a method to customize the optimisation process of the solver.
    ReconfigurationProblem
    Interface for the Reconfiguration Problem.
